Name: Wicked Tuna
Title: Game of Fins
Desc: It is the second week of the season, and a familiar boat enters the fleet, igniting old rivalries.
LongDescription: It is the second week of the bluefin tuna season; a familiar boat enters the fleet, igniting old rivalries; Pinwheel's crew members continue to mourn for Nick; the Wicked Pissah crew struggles to maintain its lead.
